query:
INSERT INTO drones (id, ip, port, region, last_checkin, checkin_by)
    VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, now(), now() + interval '15 seconds')
    ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
      ip = EXCLUDED.ip,
      port = EXCLUDED.port,
      region = EXCLUDED.region,
      last_checkin = now(),
      checkin_by = now() + interval '15 seconds';
